  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf  \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Employees are protesting for salary",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The State Engineering Corporation employees protested in front of the corporation's head office in Colombo today (29), demanding the payment of their salaries for the month of August.",
        "An engineering corporation official said that the salary for the month of August due on 25th has not yet been received.",
        "He mentioned that the salary for the month of July was paid in two parts and the second part was paid on 25th.",
        "He informed that there are no jobs for the corporation as the government has stopped the constructions for 2 years and said that action should be taken regarding the employees while taking such decisions."
      ],
